Antipattern Detected: Functional Decomposition: Using the include relationship

   Instance 1: Constructs Involved: Book Escape Room, Validate Time Slot, include (Book Escape Room → Validate Time Slot)
   Instance 1: Explanation: "Validate Time Slot" is an inclusion use case included only by "Book Escape Room." It is not associated with any actor, not included by any other use case, and does not include, extend, generalize, or get extended by any other use case. It represents a sub-step (checking slot availability) rather than a complete, independently valuable service to any actor. This is functional decomposition of the booking process into an internal validation step.

   Instance 2: Constructs Involved: Process Payment, Calculate Total Price, include (Process Payment → Calculate Total Price)
